00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:17.069
wat

00:02:17.069 --> 00:02:21.530
panelen die van rood langzaam overlopen in zwart. Dat is leuk en

00:02:21.530 --> 00:02:23.519
origineel gedaan.

00:02:23.519 --> 00:02:24.719
De 208,

00:02:24.719 --> 00:02:27.919
